snippet.title: Big Breaking: India Emerges Front Runner to host Champions Trophy If Pak Pull Out  BCCI Reply Ready
snippet.description:
2025 ICC Champions Trophy : India to host champions trophy 2025 If Pakistan Pull Out  BCCI Reply Ready 
India is now the front runner to host the Champions Trophy 2025 if Pakistan pulls out to host the tournament in February 2025.
The ICC has asked the PCB for a response about hosting the Champions Trophy in a hybrid model after India refused to travel to Pakistan. The PCB confirmed on Sunday that it received an email from the ICC about India's decision.

possession but about selflessness.

Every unspoken gesture and unseen act of kindness brings them fulfillment, as they put their beloved‚Äôs happiness above their own, showing that love is not just about being together, it‚Äôs about redefining happiness, even at the expense of their contentment.

snippet.description:

snippet.description:

Agni Official Teaser
Starring Pratik Gandhi, Divyenndu, Jitendra Joshi
Directed by Rahul Dholakia
Amazon MGM Studios presents
An Excel Entertainment production

In a city engulfed by a mysterious surge in fires, Vithal, a courageous fireman, and his brother in law, Samit, a hotshot policeman, begrudgingly join forces to unravel the escalating crisis. As they battle their own differences and a race against time, they must reconcile personal conflicts to crack the case and protect Mumbai from impending disaster.

snippet.title: The Amateur | Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Watch the trailer for #TheAmateur starring Oscar¬Æ winner Rami Malek (‚ÄúBohemian Rhapsody‚Äù) and Academy Award¬Æ nominee Laurence Fishburne (‚ÄúWhat‚Äôs Love Got to Do with It‚Äù). The all-new espionage thriller opens in theaters nationwide April 11, 2025.

Charlie Heller (Malek) is a brilliant, but deeply introverted decoder for the CIA working out of a basement office at headquarters in Langley whose life is turned upside down when his wife is killed in a London terrorist attack. When his supervisors refuse to take action, he takes matters into his own hands, embarking on a dangerous trek across the globe to track down those responsible, his intelligence serving as the ultimate weapon for eluding his pursuers and achieving his revenge. The film also stars Rachel Brosnahan, Caitr√≠ona Balfe, Jon Bernthal, Michael Stuhlbarg, Holt McCallany, Julianne Nicholson, Adrian Martinez, Danny Sapani, and Laurence Fishburne. ‚ÄúThe Amateur‚Äù is directed by James Hawes. The screenplay is by Ken Nolan and Gary Spinelli based on the novel by Robert Littell. The film is produced by Hutch Parker, p.g.a., Dan Wilson, p.g.a., Rami Malek, Joel B. Michaels, with JJ Hook serving as executive producer.
